Version 26.07
--------------
[Project]
- Versioning has been changed to calendar versioning (YY.MM)
- Re-licensed the entire project from GNU GPLv3 to WTFGPL(github.com/DS1TPT/wtfgpl), which is way more permissive.

[Program's functions]
- Added hint message when a value lesser than or greater than limit is input and minimum/maximum value has been saved instead
- Removed auto-correction during editing when data exceeds limit, as it may introduce confusion while inputting value without using backspace. The editor will auto-correct Renown only
- ESC key will cancel editing
- Save selector will display in-game date
- Fixed backspace not working properly when editing Renown
- Fixed some messages not being displayed correctly

[Code]
- pm2regen-ed will use vt100-c(github.com/DS1TPT/vt100-c) instead of original one
- Cleaned up some mess: usage of ANSI escape sequence outside of vt100 (and langPack for some cases) is now removed for better readability

